{"tid":1988092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"項明生認同六四屠城是必要的決定？","createTime":"2020-04-25T03:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T05:16:06.000Z","uid":200280,"like":65,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5ef3e72c59a364fa2dfb688f4a4c5659f85812","tid":1988092,"uid":200280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZxbMYPJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxbMYPJ.png&h=6b539687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早兩日項明生開FB post 緬懷三十年前六四屠城，覺得自己當年咁熱血其實好傻好天真，希望今年DSE 考生＂心無旁鶩＂專注考試，唔好被＂顏色＂耽誤自己大好前途<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/193367207662/posts/10157692621382663/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F193367207662%2Fposts%2F10157692621382663%2F&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=979397d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/193367207662/posts/10157692621382663/</a><br />\n<br />\n但最仆街嘅係，下邊有藍絲留言話: 當權者有他們自己的智慧，只是我們平民不能領會<br />\n<br />\n項生又即時留言大表認同啵 （見上圖）<br />\n<br />\n我想問吓項生你嘅意思係咪，當年鄧小平下令開槍屠殺學生，其實好有智慧，只係當年被坦克碌過嘅平民太蠢，不能領會鄧爺爺愛民如子嘅初心？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢啲禽獸仲想幫中共洗白，除咗DLLM我都唔知講咩好！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fa8e7efc3edd14f134421daadf9b43587bb080","tid":1988092,"uid":50894,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"耶撚：上帝有自己的智慧，只是我們平民不能領會"},{"pid":"2a8215a4e7aab3b4db724a4ed77f1a43535f757f","tid":1988092,"uid":231583,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:28:44.000Z","msg":"佢咁講法咁日本侵華南京大屠殺都係必要的決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330f8c3bf4a524f01b4d9144bad720ef9f3b5224","tid":1988092,"uid":308440,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:28:56.000Z","msg":"被篤爆左係雙面人，以家就一不做二不休，揾食緊要過扮野。 大家見到佢知點啦？上佢youtube, fb report 爆佢啦"},{"pid":"bdb0ce189d9708ea9d5ead22a862f7283e8